Chelsea Park Apartments is a perfect place to call home!
Our spacious apartments afford all of the extra conveniences you are looking for!
From the in-home washer and dryer to the kitchen with a breakfast bar, you'll be able to settle in quickly with everything you need at your fingertips.
Also featured within the kitchen is a complete appliance package (dishwasher, garbage disposal, electric stove, and refrigerator).
There are various areas in which to keep belongings organized between the entry, linen, and storage closets.
The living room can accommodate larger, sectional furniture sets and just off of it is a generously sized walk-out patio/balcony large enough for a bistro set and potted plants.
All this is comfortably maintained by central air conditioning and heat.
As a resident of our Community you will enjoy the benefits of:
